The paper deals with the problem of learning dictionaries and sparse coefficient matrices, which is a common topic in information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG). The algorithm proposed in the paper involves solving a system of linear equations, which is a fundamental problem in numerical analysis (cs.NA). The sparsity of the coefficient matrix is also a key aspect of the problem, which is relevant to the field of compressed sensing (cs.DS) and signal processing (cs.SI).
